<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-approach">1.★ <strong>靠近；接近；临近 (approach)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As the wedding day neared, I started to have second thoughts about getting married.
随着结婚日期的临近，我开始重新考虑结婚的事。</p></div></div>